## Nothing --- [Meta Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/meta_action_types/nothing) Does nothing. Can be used as a backup in case an action is not optional in some place. Type ID: `origins:nothing` --- ### Examples ```json "entity_action": { "type": "origins:nothing" } ``` This example does... nothing.
```json "bientity_action": { "type": "origins:nothing" } ``` This example... also does nothing.
